<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Music Event</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
         .song-card {
        overflow: hidden;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out, box-shadow 0.3s ease-in-out;
        border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .song-card:hover {
        transform: scale(1.05);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    }

    .song-card img {
        transition: transform 0.5s ease-in-out;
        border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
    }

    .song-card:hover img {
        transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    .song-card .btn-outline-primary {
        transition: background-color 0.3s, color 0.3s;
    }

    .song-card .btn-outline-primary:hover {
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: white;
    }

    .btn-outline-danger {
        transition: transform 0.2s ease-in-out, background-color 0.3s;
    }

    .btn-outline-danger:hover {
        transform: scale(1.1);
        background-color: #dc3545;
        color: white;
    }
        .event-banner {
            background: url('https://images.pexels.com/photos/1105666/pexels-photo-1105666.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=3600') no-repeat center center;
            background-size: cover;
            height: 100vh;
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            align-items: end;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 50px;
        }
        .event-details {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .event-date {
            color: #e74c3c;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .nav-arrows {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
        }
        .nav-arrows a {
            color: white;
            font-size: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .navbar {
            background-color: #000;
        }
        .navbar-brand {
            color: #e74c3c;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .navbar-nav .nav-link {
            color: white;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }
        .navbar-nav .nav-link:hover {
            color: #e74c3c;
        }
        .navbar-icons a {
            color: white;
            margin-left: 15px;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        .navbar-icons a:hover {
            color: #e74c3c;
        }
        .footer {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
      color: #dc3545;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #dc3545;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .footer a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
   
    /* Card hover effect */
    .card {
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .card:hover {
        transform: scale(1.05);
        box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    /* Smooth fade-in animation for cards */
    .card {
        opacity: 0;
        animation: fadeIn 1s forwards;
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
        0% {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(20px);
        }
        100% {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    }

    /* Delay for each card animation */
    .row .col:nth-child(1) .card {
        animation-delay: 0.1s;
    }

    .row .col:nth-child(2) .card {
        animation-delay: 0.2s;
    }

    .row .col:nth-child(3) .card {
        animation-delay: 0.3s;
    }

    .row .col:nth-child(4) .card {
        animation-delay: 0.4s;
    }


    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Navbar -->
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <img src="https://html.pixel-industry.com/musician/musician-html/img/svg/musician-logo-red-white.svg" alt="Logo">
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ml-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#">HOME</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#">ABOUT</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#">NEWS</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#">REVIEWS</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#">CONTACT</a></li>
                </ul>
                <div class="navbar-icons">
                    <a href="#"><i class="fas fa-shopping-cart"></i></a>
                    <a href="#"><i class="fas fa-search"></i></a>
                    <a href="#"><i class="fas fa-user"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Event Banner -->
    <div class="event-banner">
        <div class="event-details">
            <div class="event-date">MAY 21</div>
            <h2>London Music Fest 2016 Announced</h2>
            <p>AC/DC, Arctic Monkeys, Rammstein, and more</p>
            <p>Bring your friends and come to the best ever London Music Fest, June 2016. What can you expect? A lot of great artists, great music, and a lot of fun! Buy tickets today and see you at the show!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-arrows">
            <a href="#" class="prev">&#10094;</a>
            <a href="#" class="next">&#10095;</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Latest News Section -->
    <section class="latest-news py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="text-center mb-5" style="color: #e74c3c;">Latest News</h2>
            <div class="row">
                <!-- Main news article -->
                <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                    <div class="card border-0">
                        <img src="https://html.pixel-industry.com/musician/musician-html/img/blog/music-blog-post-01.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Main News Image">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">AC/DC’s singer Brian Johnson stop touring, Axl Rose is new frontman</h5>
                            <p class="card-text text-muted">BY: Musician | News | 3 hours ago</p>
                            <p class="card-text">One of the most popular groups in the world has a new frontman. After doctor’s orders, their frontman Brian Johnson had to stop touring. It’s been confirmed that Axl Rose is [...]</p>
